metadata.name: Forgettable
metadata.description:
Unforgettable women,
Whose legacies still endure,
Their stories we retell again,
And their courage we still adore.

Their strength and perseverance,
Through struggles they did face,
Their achievements we still reverence,
And the paths they paved with grace.

From leaders and pioneers,
To artists and activists too,
Their impact still inspires,
As they showed us what we can do.

Their voices echo through the ages,
A reminder of their worth,
Their legacy lives on in stages,
As they continue to shape the earth.

Unforgettable women,
Their stories never fade,
Their memory an inspiration,
To live with passion and not be afraid.
